Package: fluorojip
Type: Package
Title: Compute Chlorophyll a Fluorescence OJIP Parameters
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Joao", "Everthon", "da Silva Ribeiro",
           email = "j.everthon@hotmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Ronald", "Maldonado", "Rodriguez",
           role = "aut")    
    person("Toshik", "Iarley", "da Silva",
           role = "aut"),
  )
Description: Compute chlorophyll a fluorescence OJIP / JIP-test parameters
    from raw fluorescence summary data (Fo, Fm, O-J-I-P steps, area).
    Includes standard PSII performance indices and fluxes per reaction center
    and per cross section. Provides helpers to import Handy PEA exports and
    tools for exploratory visualization (heatmaps and 3D plots).
